Upcoming event: Giving Food to the Homeless - November 21, 2015
What do you usually do on Saturday night? Go for coffee with friends? Chat-chit? Spend time with your family??? Yes, a lot of things to do. BUT WE HAVE A VERY SPECIAL PROGRAM FOR YOU TO JOIN: Giving Food to the Homeless on Saturday night November 21, 2015 (17:00 we prepare the food; 21:00 we go out and deliver to the homeless around HCMC) 

Hereunder is our same previous event: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HdNCx1uzXCg&feature=share
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0i55Usqmq8U

The Compassion in Vietnam Club will organize this event again to give food to the homeless. We will cook chicken soup and deliver to homeless in HCMC also to the people who work during the night. It will be great if you can join us as volunteer to support the cooking and delivery, and also we are welcome all donations to this meaningful event. So, COME and JOIN with us!!!!! Register via the Event Link or send mesg to our FB. 

Contact: 
Ms. Keiko Le (ĐT: 090 6922314)
Ms. Truong Tri Thuy Hanh (ĐT: 091 8041804)
Ms. Phuoc Hong (ĐT: 093 6395477)